</p><h2><img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzY5NjUwNjAucG5n/original/DleY6m.png" loading="lazy">&nbsp;RELATIONS<img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzY5NjUwNTcucG5n/original/flr83Z.png" loading="lazy"></h2><p><iframe frameborder="0" src="https://itch.io/embed/3414319?bg_color=181817&fg_color=d6bd6c&border_color=181817" width="552" height="167">&lt;a href=&quot;<a href="https://merchant-shade.itch.io/16x16-puny-dungeon">Free&quot; class=&quot;redactor-linkify-object&quot;&gt;https://merchant-shade.itch.io/16x16-puny-dungeon&quot;&gt;Free</a> 16x16 Puny Dungeon Tileset by Shade&lt;/a&gt;</iframe><iframe frameborder="0" src="https://itch.io/embed/1549998?bg_color=181817&fg_color=d6bd6c&border_color=181817" width="552" height="167">&lt;a href=&quot;<a href="https://merchant-shade.itch.io/16x16-puny-characters-plus-sprites">16x16&quot; class=&quot;redactor-linkify-object&quot;&gt;https://merchant-shade.itch.io/16x16-puny-characters-plus-sprites&quot;&gt;16x16</a> Puny Characters Editor Edition by Shade&lt;/a&gt;</iframe><br></p>
