t="{&quot;user_id&quot;:6434390,&quot;id&quot;:16054982}" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div id="first-post" class="post_anchor"></div><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_up" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_down" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/sanchobouillant"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/sanchobouillant">sanchobouillant</a></span><span title="2026-05-09 14:19:41" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/16054982">7 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p><strong>This is AWESOME!!!!! Does anyone have some animal tiles with the same vibe?</strong>
 </p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" class="post_action reply_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div id="post-15609129" data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:7399096,&quot;id&quot;:15609129}" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_up" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_down" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/darkest-dreams"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzIzMjE3MTM1LnBuZw==/25x25%23/SpdZhc.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/darkest-dreams">Sleepless Entity</a></span><span title="2026-03-01 10:27:43" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15609129">76 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Are you planning to add the dead trees like you have in the Mini pack? If not, I can just use those. &nbsp;Was just curious. (:</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" class="post_action reply_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div id="post-15417020" data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:12273058,&quot;id&quot;:15417020}" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_up" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_down" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/anpd"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-gold.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/anpd">anpd</a></span><span title="2026-02-06 16:00:02" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15417020">99 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Looks great, any plans to add more biomes to the tileset?</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" class="post_action reply_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-15427934" data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:3114458,&quot;id&quot;:15427934}" class="community_post is_reply has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_up" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_down" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/merchant-shade"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzEyNTc3Njg0LnBuZw==/25x25%23/LjJj4M.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/merchant-shade">Shade</a></span><span title="2026-02-08 14:24:59" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15427934">97 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>yeahh im working on snow and desert rn ^^</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" class="post_action reply_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies"><div id="post-15430271" data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:12273058,&quot;id&quot;:15430271}" class="community_post is_reply has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_up" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_down" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/anpd"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-gold.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/anpd">anpd</a></span><span title="2026-02-08 18:56:31" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15430271">97 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Nice :) will keep an eye out! Some small mountains would be great also&nbsp;:D</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" class="post_action reply_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="post-13330944" data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:1100010,&quot;id&quot;:13330944}" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_up" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_down" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/alasseearfalas"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzExNTQ2NDI1LnBuZw==/25x25%23/R34PGM.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/alasseearfalas">Alassë Eärfalas</a></span><span title="2025-07-12 02:23:33" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/13330944">309 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Hi there! I love your work, and I&nbsp;have a question.&nbsp;</p><p>What are the odds of you making a version of this pack&nbsp;with the same colors you used for&nbsp;Miniworld? I&nbsp;love all the details&nbsp;of this updated version,&nbsp;but I really miss the brighter colors.&nbsp;Your Miniworld pack inspires me every time I see it, and I&#x27;m sure this pack would do the same if it shared the&nbsp;same palette. :)</p><p>Thank you so much for sharing such wonderful assets! I really hope I&#x27;ll get to use them someday. :)</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" class="post_action reply_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-13331821" data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:3114458,&quot;id&quot;:13331821}" class="community_post is_reply has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_up" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_down" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/merchant-shade"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzEyNTc3Njg0LnBuZw==/25x25%23/LjJj4M.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/merchant-shade">Shade</a></span><span title="2025-07-12 06:47:51" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/13331821">308 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>A brighter version which has the same brightness/color with miniworld&#x27;s grass&nbsp;would look like this:&nbsp;<a href="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/736816018336252057/1393482218659119275/image.png?ex=687354f2&is=68720372&hm=e7df67719c23a76c071a9cd5223a07643198185982aba98c7b3ece679ed2d156&=&format=webp&quality=lossless&width=386&height=930" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">Puny-Light-Version</a>&nbsp;(let me know if u cant access the image)&nbsp;:)<br></p><p>Punyworld&#x27;s colors are much more... standard i guess? Ive had issues with making new colors/new stuff for miniworld because it was too bright.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" class="post_action reply_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies"><div id="post-13337653" data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:1100010,&quot;id&quot;:13337653}" class="community_post is_reply has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_up" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_down" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/alasseearfalas"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzExNTQ2NDI1LnBuZw==/25x25%23/R34PGM.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/alasseearfalas">Alassë Eärfalas</a></span><span title="2025-07-13 06:08:42" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/13337653">307 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Ah, I&nbsp;see. That makes sense. :) I&nbsp;personally really love the brighter grass &amp;&nbsp;terrain colors, but I&nbsp;can see that it really doesn&#x27;t work with the buildings and bridges. Oh well; nothing stopping me from tweaking the colors myself, haha.&nbsp;</p><p>Thanks for getting back to me so quick! And thanks again for making and sharing these assets, they are super lovely and I&nbsp;hope to make a game with them someday. :) Cheers!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" class="post_action reply_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="post-11435174" data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:3608324,&quot;id&quot;:11435174}" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_up" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmerchant-shade.itch.io%2F16x16-puny-world&amp;intent=community"><svg aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_vote_down" width="20" role="img" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/ldek"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzEyMjM0NDk2LnBuZw==/25x25%23/ijcOAT.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/ldek">IllFatedStudios</a></span><span title="2024-11-23 19:18:14" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/11435174">1 year ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</s